<html>
<head>
<title>ACLU Briefing Papers</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor=#FFFFFF>
<blockquote>
<IMG SRC="/graphics/libraryhdr.gif"><P>
<center><h1>ACLU Briefing Papers</h1></center>
<br>
Number 1 -- <a href="/library/pbp1.html">Guardian of Liberty</a><br>
Number 2 -- <a href="/library/pbp2.html">Crime and Civil Liberties</a><br>
Number 3 -- <a href="/library/pbp3.html">Church and State </a><br>
Number 4 -- <a href="/library/pbp4.html">Lie Detector Testing </a><br>
Number 5 -- <a href="/library/pbp5.html">Drug Testing and the Workplace</a><br>
Number 6 -- <a href="/library/pbp6.html">"English Only"</a><br>
Number 7 -- <a href="/library/pbp7.html">Repreductive Freedom: The Rights of Minors</a><br>
Number 8 -- <a href="/library/pbp8.html">The Death Penalty</a><br>
