<HEAD>
<TITLE>Mailing List Description</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">
<BLOCKQUOTE><IMG SRC="/graphics/actionhdr.gif" ALT="[ACLU]">
<CENTER>
<H1>The ACLU's Mailing Lists</H1></CENTER>
<H3><A NAME="campus">The Campus Mailing List</A> </H3>
<P>Offered to ACLU Campus groups and campus activists, this list was created
for the discussion of civil liberties organizing and civil liberties issues on
college campuses.  All participants in this list are asked to identify their
college or ACLU affiliation in all messages.  This list can be joined via the
web  site or via email by writing to majordomo@aclu.org with subscribe campus 
in the message body.  Any text on the subject line will be ignored.
</P>
<P></P>
<H3><A NAME="schedule">ACLU on AOL Newsletter (Schedule)</A></H3>
<P>A weekly newsletter highlighting the ACLU's forum on America Online.
Includes updates of online contests on AOL, live programming and new content.
</P>
<P>This list can be joined via the the ACLU's Constitution Hall on AOL (keyword
ACLU), the web site or via email by writing to majordomo@aclu.org with subscribe
schedule in the body of the message.  Any text on the subject line will be
ignored.
</P>
<P></P>
<H3><A NAME="action">The ACLU Legislative Network (Action)</A></H3>
<P>The ACLU Legislative Network is a periodic alert on specific bills or issues
affecting civil liberties before Congress and the Executive Branch.  This list
can be joined via the web  site or via email by writing to majordomo@aclu.org
with subscribe  action in the body of the message.  Any text on the subject line
will be ignored.
</P>
<P></P>
<H3><A NAME="cyber">The ACLU Cyber-Liberties Update</A> </H3>
<P>The biweekly newsletter ACLU Cyber-Liberties Update, covers legislative,
litigation, and industry issues in new communications technology and their
impact on civil liberties. This list can be joined via the web site or via email
by writing to  majordomo@aclu.org with subscribe cyber-liberties in the body of
the  message.  Any text in the subject will be ignored.
</P>
<P></P>

<H3><A NAME="news">The ACLU NewsFeed</A></H3>
<P>ACLU News Releases will be a newsfeed of ACLU national and affiliate news. 
Subscribers can expect 1-5 items weekly.  This list  can be joined via the web
site or via email by writing to  majordomo@aclu.org, with subscribe news in the
body of your message.  Any text in the subject line will be ignored.
</P>
<P></P></BLOCKQUOTE>
<CENTER><A HREF="/graphics/toolbar.map"><IMG
SRC="/graphics/toolbar.gif" ISMAP="ISMAP" BORDER="0"></A>
