<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Death Penalty</TITLE>
</HEAD> 
<BODY BGCOLOR="#ffffff">
<CENTER>
<IMG SRC="/graphics/death.gif">
</CENTER>
<P>

</P>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<H3>ACLU Press Releases</H3>
<UL><LI><A HREF="http://www.aclu.org/news/pressind.html#death"><B>CLICK HERE
TO SEE THE LATEST PRESS RELEASE</B></A></LI></UL>
<H4>1996</H4>
<UL><LI><A HREF="http://www.aclu.org/news/n041896c.html">04/18/96: NYCLU
Files Suit Challenging Removal of DA in Death Penalty Case</A><BR>
</LI>
<LI>
<A HREF="http://www.aclu.org/news/n012296b.html">
1/22 -- Death Row Prisoner To Face Firing Squad In Utah; ACLU,                  
    Rights Groups Mobilize Opposition</A><BR></LI>
</UL>
<H4>1995</H4>
<UL>
<LI>
<A HREF="http://www.aclu.org/news/n031095.html">
3/10 -- Governor Weld 'Perpetrating Fraud' by Advocating Death Penalty; Civil
Liberties Union of      Massachusetts Descries State Crime Proposals 
</A><BR>
</LI>
<LI>
<A HREF="http://www.aclu.org/news/n021695.html">
2/16 -- New York Civil Liberties Union Says No to Death Penalty: 'Immoral in
Principal; Unfair and      Discriminatory in Practice' </A>
</LI>
</UL>
</BLOCKQUOTE> 
