<HEAD>
<TITLE>Statewide Anti-Gay Marriage Laws</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="ffffff">
<P></P>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="/graphics/gay.gif">     </CENTER>

<H2 ALIGN="CENTER">Statewide Anti-gay Marriage Laws<BR><I>(as of December 4,
1996)</I>
</H2>
<P><B>States Passed (16)</B>: Alaska, Arizona, Delaware, Georgia, Idaho,
Illinois, Kansas, Michigan, Missouri, North Carolina, Oklahoma, Pennsylvania,
South Carolina, South Dakota, Tennessee, Utah
</P>
<P><B>States Blocked (20)</B>: Alabama, California, Colorado, Florida, Hawaii,
Iowa, Kentucky, Louisiana, Maine, Maryland, Minnesota, Mississippi, New Mexico,
New York, Rhode Island, Virginia, Washington, West Virginia, Wisconsin, Wyoming
</P>
<P></P>
