</P></DD>
<DD><A HREF="/news/n071696b.html">July 16, 1996 -- ACLU Calls on Congress To
Kick Wiretap Habit And Eliminate 'Stealth Funding' For Digital Telephony
</A><BR>
</DD>
<DD><A HREF="http://www.aclu.org/congress/telltr.html">January 29, 1996 -- Why
the Telecom Bill Should Be Rejected  
</A></DD>
