<BLOCKQUOTE>



<HR>
<CENTER>
<H3>                        ACLU Cyber-Liberties Update<BR>
                        Wednesday, February 5, 1996 </H3>
</CENTER>					   
<HR>

<B>CONTENTS:</B> 
<P>
