<CENTER><h3>
                        ACLU Cyber-Liberties Update<BR>
                        Wednesday, January 22, 1997</H3> 
</CENTER>					   
<HR>

<P>
<B>CONTENTS:</B>
  
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="#reno"> Reno v. ACLU Update: Government's Brief Asserts Unprecedented
  Powers to criminalize Online Speech</A>
<LI><A href="#ala"> ACLU Files Suit against New York State Internet Censorship Law</A>
<LI><A HREF="#ga">Georgia Internet Case Update</A>
<LI><A href="#nwu">Northwestern University Defends Free Speech on the Internet</A>
