<H3>                        <CENTER>ACLU Cyber-Liberties Update<BR>
                        Wednesday, November 27, 1996</CENTER> </H3>
					   

<HR>

<H3>CONTENTS: </H3>

<UL TYPE=DISC>
	<LI> <A HREF="#editor">Note From the Editor</A>
	<LI> <A HREF="#ga">Plaintiffs File Reply Brief in Georgia Internet Case</A>
