<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>


Cyberliberties


</TITLE>


</HEAD>

<body bgcolor="ffffffff">

<table border>

<tr><td colspan=2><br>

<center><img src="/graphics/update.gif" ><h3>November 8, 1995</h3></center>

</td></tr>

<br>

<tr><td colspan=2><h3><br><blockquote><center><font color="3300ff">A bi-weekly e-zine on cyber-liberties cases and controversies

at the state and federal level.</font></h3></center></blockquote></td></tr>

<p>



<tr><td><center><img src="/graphics/compute.gif"></td>



<td>

<blockquote><br>

<a href="cyb1108b.html#entry">ACLU Statement and ACTION ALERT on Federal Wiretap Bill</a>

<p>

<a href="cyb1108b.html#act">ACTION ALERT on Federal Online Indecency Legislation</a>

<p>

 <a href="cyb1108b.html#state">State Utility Commissions Consider Online Access and Privacy Issues</a>

