<HEAD>
<TITLE>
HIV / AIDS 
</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#ffffff">
<CENTER>
<IMG SRC="/graphics/aids.gif"> 
</CENTER>
<P>

 
</P>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<P><B>
</B></P>
<DL>
<DT><B>
ACLU Papers 
</B></DT>
<DD>
<A HREF="/library/pbp13.html"><B>AIDS and Civil Liberties</B></A>   
<P>
</P></DD>
<DT><B>The ACLU on. . .</B></DT>
<DD><A HREF="newborn.html"><B>HIV Testing of Newborns</B></A>
<P></P></DD>
<DT>
<B>ACLU in Congress 
</B></DT>
<DD>
<A HREF="http://www.aclu.org/congress/hiv1.html"><B>February 9, 1996 --
Talking Points on the Dornan Amendment to Mandate the Immediate       Discharge
of All HIV-Positive Service Members </B></A> 
<P>
</P></DD>
<DD>
<A HREF="http://www.aclu.org/congress/hiv2.html"><B>February 8, 1996 -- Letter
to ACLU Affiliates from Gene Guerrero &amp; Alexander Robinson Regarding HIV &amp;
Military Personnel </B></A> 
<P>
 
</P></DD>
<DT><B>ACLU in Court</B></DT>
<DD><A HREF="/court/givens.html"><B>Givens v. South Carolina -- Exclusion of
AIDS Patients from State Insurance Pool</B></A></DD></DL>
<P></P></BLOCKQUOTE>
