http://www.aclu.org:80/issues/worker/iswr.html 204.243.96.55 19970213122020 text/html 1771
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Thursday, 13-Feb-97 12:19:09 GMT
