http://www.aclu.org:80/issues/gay/gaystor.html 204.243.96.55 19970213141321 text/html 4701
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Thursday, 13-Feb-97 14:12:03 GMT
