<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Lucie McKinney Story</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR=#FFFFFF>
<blockquote>
<img src="/graphics/courthdr.gif">
<CENTER><H2>ACLU Client - Lucie McKinney</H2></CENTER>
<img src="/graphics/mckin.jpg" align=left><blockquote><font size=4>
The widow of Republican Congressman Stewart McKinney, Lucie established a
foundation to assist people with AIDS.  When the McKinney Foundation bought a
house and sought permission to make it a residence for HIV-infected homeless
people, townspeople's objections prompted local officials to turn the
application down.  McKinney won her lawsuit, filed under the Fair Housing Act
and the Americans With Disabilities Act.</font>
<P></blockquote>
<br clear=all><br>

</blockquote>    


