<TITLE>Elizabeth  & Milo Sheff Story</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR=#FFFFFF>
<blockquote>
<img src="/graphics/courthdr.gif">
<CENTER><H2>ACLU Client - Elizabeth and Milo Sheff</H2></CENTER>
<font size=4>
<img src="/graphics/sheff.jpg" align=left><blockquote>Milo Sheff and his mother Elizabeth are lead plaintiffs in a continuing
"educational equity" lawsuit brought by the ACLU against racial and economic
disparities in their local public school system.  Their suit, the first to
seek desegregation across school district lines, invokes the state
constitution's guarantee of an "adequate education" for every child.</font>
</blockquote><P>

