<TITLE>75th Anniversary</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY bgcolor=#ffffff>
<center><h2>1995 ACLU BIENNIAL CONFERENCE<br></h2>

<h4>
New York City<br>
June 20-25, 1995<br>
<p>
<B>CONFERENCE PROGRAM</B><p>
<hr width=50%>
</center></h4>
<blockquote>
<B>THURSDAY, JUNE 22</B><br>
