<BLOCKQUOTE>



 


<TABLE BORDER="1" CELLPADDING="4" CELLSPACING="4" WIDTH="90%">
<TR ALIGN=CENTER>
	<TD ALIGN=CENTER COLSPAN="2"><H3>Banned Books Week</H3>
</TD>
</TR>


<TR>

<TD>

<B> Celebrating the Literature Others Have Tried to Suppress</B></CENTER>
<P>
<P>
Banned Books Week is a time to celebrate literature and art and examine the strains of intolerance and repression that continue to haunt our society.
</P>

<P>
While many people see book censorship as a thing of the past, or an infrequent occurrence, it is neither. Books with clear artistic and cultural merit are still challenged frequently by those who want to control what others read. Permitting restraints on any expression sets the stage for attacks on all expression that is artistically or politically controversial or that portrays some of society's unpleasant features.  Whatever the reason, censorship must be fought whenever it arises.
    
</P> 
<P>
Censorship today comes in many forms. Whenever a school board, librarian, politician or store owner limits your right to decide what you want to see, hear or read, that is censorship.
</P>

<P>
The ACLU opposes all forms of censorship. We believe that people should decide for themselves. For 200 years the right to choose what to see and hear has been one of our most cherished freedoms.
</P>

<P>
Fight book banning and censorship when it happens in your community,  and exercise your right to read the books that others would ban out of fear.
</P>
</TD>
<TD width=25%>
<P>
<B>What you'll find here:</B><P>

	<A HREF="order.html">Order banned books online</A><BR>Exercise your right to read the books that others have tried to block.<P>
	<A HREF="howmany.html">How many of these banned books have <I>you</I> read?</A><BR> We're curious.<P>
	<A HREF="bbwmatch.html">Guess why these books were banned</A><BR> We'll give you a book, and a list of reasons given for censoring. Can you match the reason to the book?<P>
	<A HREF="bbwlinks.html">Other online resources on banned books and censorship</A><BR>

</TD>
</TR>
</TABLE>
</BLOCKQUOTE>
