			<H4>
				These expert witnesses and plaintiffs will be in court with the ACLU to support free expression on the Internet. HERE'S HOW YOU CAN HELP THIS HISTORIC EFFORT.
			</H4>
			<P>
			The single most important thing you can do is provide financial support for this critical and costly litigation.
			</P>
